<p>After you have created a catalogue, map the market’s data fields to item data saved in plentymarkets. This chapter describes how you map data fields and what particularities apply for item exports to bol.com.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="data-field-mappings">4.2.1. Mapping data fields in the catalogue</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>After you have created a catalogue, map the market’s data fields to item data saved in plentymarkets. Check the documentation of the sales channel to find out what data the market expects for the individual data fields.</p>
