<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="900">6.2. Automatically sending cancellations</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Set up an <a href="/en/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically inform bol.com of cancellations. Whenever you are dealing with cancellations, you need to send bol.com a reason for the cancellation. Open the <strong>Setup » Orders » Status</strong> menu and create additional order statuses as needed. The following cancellation reasons can be transferred to bol.com:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Out of stock</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
